        "title": "Resources",
        "intro": "The mark is personal. The movement is collective. These organizations are building the culture we believe in — inclusive, informed, and unafraid. We also include the stuff gun culture skips: safe storage, mental health resources, and honest information about risk. Bookmark the ones that speak to you.",
